{"tid":529534,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix 是 Stand-up Comedy 兵家之地","createTime":"2018-01-15T00:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T03:43:34.000Z","uid":78390,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"526b5a8229ec8ef4a9bf0eccbea2470b45d53ee4","tid":529534,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T00:53:29.000Z","msg":"Netflix除咗多戲多劇之如<br />\n佢地都經常重金禮聘唔同棟篤笑明星 幫佢地開Show <br />\n好多都好搞笑而且讓人反思嘅地方<br />\n大慨一粒左右 放鬆之如我認為可以學好多野係每個special<br />\n鐘意黃子華都應該會鐘意睇嘅<br />\n<br />\nDave Chappelle<br />\n可算係棟篤界失蹤咗十年嘅巨星<br />\nNetflix 係佢再出山之地<br />\n佢Netflix special 都係評論時事尤其transgender 同最近#Metoo 係好好笑<br />\n加上佢對自己種族充滿熱情 有時都俾佢講嘅野打動<br />\nDave Chappelle: Equanimity &amp; The Bird Revelation<br />\nDave Chappelle: The Age of Spin<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/084122_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F084122_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=41284e85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTom Segura<br />\n最近出咗新Stand-up 正到仆街<br />\n呢個比較係揭開人性醜惡一面<br />\n加上獨特棟篤技巧 Delivery簡直係100分<br />\n<br />\nTom Segura: Disgraceful<br />\nTom Segura: Completely Normal<br />\nTom Segura: Mostly Stories<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/084058_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F084058_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f1539179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAnthony Jeselnik<br />\n雖然得一個special<br />\n不過佢啲笑位簡直挑戰道德底線<br />\n經常攞死做笑點 <br />\n簡直笑完會落地獄<br />\n<br />\nAnthony Jeselnik: Thoughts ans Prayers<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/084152_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F084152_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9066dc8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAziz Ansari<br />\n佢賣點係講現代愛情<br />\n比較貼近年輕人嘅主題<br />\n不過今日好似俾人指控sexual harassment<br />\n希望唔會打底佢事業<br />\n<br />\nAziz Ansari: Buried Alive<br />\nAziz Ansari Live at Madison Square Garden<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/084224_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F084224_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=95fe3c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBill Burr<br />\n成日亂嗡當秘笈<br />\n不過都一個好好棟篤明星 籍得一試<br />\n<br />\nBill Burr: Walk Your Way out<br />\nBill Burr: I'm sorry you feel that way<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/084331_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F084331_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8d7f903f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJoe Rogan<br />\n好多人都有聽過佢podcast<br />\n佢over the top delivery 都真係好搞笑<br />\n又講食大麻諗到嘅 ideas真係好好笑<br />\n<br />\nJoe Rogan: Triggered<br />\nJoe Rogan: Live<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/084400_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F084400_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=53594d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJim Gaffigan<br />\n懶人一定要睇<br />\n次次都係個懶人會做嘅野<br />\n睇完會發覺原來大家都好懶<br />\n<br />\nJim Gaffigan: Cinco<br />\nJim Gaffigan: Obsessed<br />\nJim Gaffigan: Beyond the Pale<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/084436_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F084436_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7680af3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多例如Bo Burnham用音樂做楝篤<br />\nLouis C.K 不過metoo咗 唔介紹住<br />\nRussle Peter<br />\n仲有好多 又咩好介紹巴打"},{"pid":"061f48840452bf6e942dd7a1d05f3cace708bd8a","tid":529534,"uid":142225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:08:27.000Z","msg":"fluffy都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c897b572599df166f535ac8f6dab91857916db","tid":529534,"uid":48497,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"仲有港產代表：卓韻芝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f28a36d18a5258aac6607f13eacb735cfd16382","tid":529534,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed88e4b9e16d653d06e88eddf8672a9fa8f9ebbc","tid":529534,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"Louis C.K<br />\n量產咗之後無咁好笑"},{"pid":"f679d71b582f18db8fb0b6bf68317a377f352e05","tid":529534,"uid":126044,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ed88e4b9e16d653d06e88eddf8672a9fa8f9ebbc","tid":529534,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"Louis C.K<br />\n量產咗之後無咁好笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:58:46.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n佢d delivery都係好正<br />\n但d內容真係普通<br />\n<br />\n反而之前唔識野<br />\n以為Dave chappelle 講野一味誇張<br />\n直到上年Netflix上佢個兩套<br />\n成個show有結構，有中心思想<br />\n新出個兩集又係正<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;So I kick her in ther pussy&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7808938c15090a0ded30b85ed722b245006f2ee3","tid":529534,"uid":115539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T10:33:59.000Z","msg":"Bill Burr <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"